results.name: Restricted growth functions for set partitions.
comment: There are restricted growth functions (RGF, sometime called restricted growth strings, RGS) for various kinds of combinatorial objects.  For the RGF used here see figure 17.1-D on p.358 of the Fxtbook, see links.
